WEBVTT

00:02:58.680 --> 00:03:00.096
Even soundex,

00:03:00.120 --> 00:03:04.536
a standard method for grouping words
by how similar they sound,

00:03:04.560 --> 00:03:06.136
was not good enough.

00:03:06.160 --> 00:03:07.856
So we had to modify it

00:03:07.880 --> 00:03:11.680
to help us link and match
existing records.

00:03:14.160 --> 00:03:15.360
Before the iPhone,

00:03:16.040 --> 00:03:19.856
software engineers
developed for personal computers,

00:03:19.880 --> 00:03:21.136
but from our experience,

00:03:21.160 --> 00:03:24.536
we knew our power system
is not reliable enough

00:03:24.560 --> 00:03:25.840
for personal computers.

00:03:26.480 --> 00:03:31.136
So we repurposed touch screen
point-of-sale terminals